title: Quality of Life
subtitle: How You Want Your Life to Be
on-arrival: progress = 13

Facilyn takes a long sip of her tea.

Facilyn: Now we come to the heart of it all — your Quality of Life Statement. 

Facilyn: Think of it as your collective sense of what you most value and how you want your life to be.

Facilyn: We will consider multiple areas like economic well-being, relationships, challenge and growth, and purpose and contribution. 

- #qol_intro

